No. 1325,

Misc.

Jimenez et al. v. Naff, Yakima County Auditor, et al. Michael Rosen, Thomas H. S. Brucker, Pete Tijerina, and Mario Obledo for appellants. Slade Gorton, Attorney General, and Robert J. Doran and Donald H. Brazier, Jr., Deputy Attorneys General, for appellees State of Washington et al.

Appeal from D. C. E. D. Wash. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Probable jurisdiction noted and case transferred to appellate docket.
